{"tid":1048996,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［又關強國事］外來種昆蟲入侵日本多地櫻花","createTime":"2019-03-06T03:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T07:01:16.000Z","uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4823957f094d7b497de17c41f2379de18be4f5","tid":1048996,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"春季漸漸接近，相信有不少人都非常期待櫻花盛開的美景。但日本櫻花近年受外來種昆蟲「クビアカツヤカミキリ」（首赤艶天牛）入侵，現時東京都、大阪府等7個都府縣已確認外來種。受「首赤艶天牛」侵食的樹木不會開花之餘，嚴重更會枯死。為保護櫻花樹，除了用網圍住樹木之外，有地方更計劃用獎金、獎品吸引市民，希望可以成功消滅害蟲。<br />\n<br />\n據日本傳媒報道，最近日本有些景點的櫻花樹用藍色網圍起，實情是為了阻隔一種名為「首赤艶天牛」外來種昆蟲。「首赤艶天牛」本來<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>來自中國、越南一帶</strong></span>，7年前首次在愛知縣發現，現時栃木縣、群馬縣、埼玉縣、東京都、愛知縣、大阪府及德島縣7個都府縣已確認此品種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20190304140940__vlcsnap-2019-03-04-14h07m27s549.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20190304140940__vlcsnap-2019-03-04-14h07m27s549.png&h=c194841b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20190304140941__vlcsnap-2019-03-04-14h07m34s796.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20190304140941__vlcsnap-2019-03-04-14h07m34s796.png&h=af113a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「首赤艶天牛」一如其名，以頸部呈紅色為特徵。牠們特別喜歡櫻花樹，幼蟲會攢進樹木並咀嚼成粉。幼蟲會在樹幹中生活2年，期間會蠶食樹木內部。樹木變虛弱就會不開花，嚴重者更會令樹木枯萎<br />\n<br />\n當中群馬縣一間高校外共28棵櫻花樹全被「首赤艶天牛」入侵，為了防止樹木倒塌，校方忍痛斬去其中6棵櫻花樹。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20190304140945__vlcsnap-2019-03-04-14h08m20s960.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20190304140945__vlcsnap-2019-03-04-14h08m20s960.png&h=34aaa38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時除了捕獲害蟲及以網圍起樹木保護以外，群馬縣館林市市長打算有新「作戰計劃」：凡每成功捕殺一隻「首赤艶天牛」，將送保礦力或50日圓作為獎勵。（注意「首赤艶天牛」不可徒手捕捉，否則會被咬傷）<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/26646/外來種昆蟲入侵日本多地櫻花-市長出動獎金獎品懸賞消滅害蟲/4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F26646%2F%E5%A4%96%E4%BE%86%E7%A8%AE%E6%98%86%E8%9F%B2%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E6%AB%BB%E8%8A%B1-%E5%B8%82%E9%95%B7%E5%87%BA%E5%8B%95%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91%E7%8D%8E%E5%93%81%E6%87%B8%E8%B3%9E%E6%B6%88%E6%BB%85%E5%AE%B3%E8%9F%B2%2F4&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXnjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=e9f5699b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/26646/外來種昆蟲入侵日本多地櫻花-市長出動獎金獎品懸賞消滅害蟲/4</a><br />\n<br />\n得喇，地球係你架喇，收返d蟲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b3dac1d013f7209592a22d9d998a993db39f82","tid":1048996,"uid":5218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"一黎就黎隻針對櫻花既害蟲，睇黎有 d 野。"},{"pid":"35ca7877d63ea8abb6e1b5e1d5e714d6101503f8","tid":1048996,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"我屌咁撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d40d8934f3d55c91a5ffb7cdf492097c88e29cc","tid":1048996,"uid":221827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61b3dac1d013f7209592a22d9d998a993db39f82","tid":1048996,"uid":5218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"一黎就黎隻針對櫻花既害蟲，睇黎有 d 野。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"蝗禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06515e61ef6866371bab545e8d496ad802a54f3","tid":1048996,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}